import axios from 'axios';
 
// let axiosInstance = axios;
 
// export function initHttp(config) {
//   axiosInstance = axios.create(config);
// }
 
let _instance = null;
 
class Http {
	get instance() {
		if (!_instance) {
			throw new Error('Use init() to initialize new instance.');
		}
		return _instance;
	}
	init(config) {
		if (_instance) {
			throw new Error('Cannot initialize new instance twice.');
		}
		_instance = axios.create(config);
	}
}
 
export default new Http();
